00:35:33.920 --> 00:35:39.700
of managing ranks of machines which move through classrooms.

00:35:39.699 --> 00:35:46.029
So, there's another example of how consumer
viewpoint is changing the products to reduce costs

00:35:46.030 --> 00:35:50.390
because now the teachers can manage the systems.

00:35:52.860 --> 00:35:54.460
Self service management.

