00:38:50.639 --> 00:38:54.289
when it's suitable for them, and they can do it themselves.

00:38:54.289 --> 00:38:57.059
There's less down time to them.

00:38:57.059 --> 00:39:02.199
IT is now allowed to focus on the
things that bring value to the business.

00:39:03.269 --> 00:39:11.780
